INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (56201, 'There has been more bloodshed in the name of God than for any other cause. And it is all because people never attempt to reach the fountain-head. They are content only to comply with the customs of their forefathers, and want others to do the same.', 2874, 0), (56202, 'Detach yourself from people that only exists when they need something from you. From people who only calls you a “friend” when they have favors and leave you behind afterwards. Remove toxic people in your life, they will become a hindrance to you.', 12701, 0), (56203, 'Most of the modern human society has nearly lost the faculty of observing the internal mechanism.', 2874, 0), (56204, 'True religion must raise to work at the bar and the bench, on the couch and on the streets, in the cottage of the poor man and in the penthouse of the entrepreneur, with the fisherman that is catching fish and with the students that are studying.', 2874, 0), (56205, 'Time spent in assessing one''s self, is the time spent best.', 2874, 0), (56206, 'Never waste your precious time in discussing the good and bad qualities of others.', 2874, 0), (56207, 'The Self, when finite, is Human and when infinite, is God.', 2874, 0), (56208, 'Infinite and finite are both mental constructs.', 2874, 0), (56209, 'Nature of Human is neither good nor bad, it is simply a fusion of primitive instinctual urges and modern humane conscience.', 2874, 0), (56210, 'There are pearls in the deepest fathoms of the Self, but to get them you will have to go through unimaginable perils.', 2874, 0), (56211, 'You don''t always get to know what happened, or why things happened a certain way, but it always, always, goes deeper than any one thing.', 7554, 0), (56212, 'A rich life is lived from a giving heart not a selfish mind.', 4889, 0), (56213, 'You are either the person you were or the person you are, eventually you have to let go of one', 2891, 0), (56214, 'But the amazing thing about life, I''ve finally discovered, is that you really don''t learn from past mistakes. You do logically, reasonably, but emotionally not for a second.', 12702, 0), (56215, 'Dare to contradict the scientist, not because of your scripture, but because of your own rational thinking.', 2874, 0), (56216, 'Human brain is structured to avoid any kind of refutation of one''s religious beliefs.', 2874, 0), (56217, 'Stop nourishing other people’s ideas and beliefs in your life. Take up your own idea and endeavor to accomplish it.', 2874, 0), (56218, 'Life does not change if you only modify the content, your life will change if you will dare to alter the context.', 88, 0), (56219, 'Everything that humans have achieved until now, were once merely an imagination in someone’s head.', 2874, 0), (56220, 'Shred the fake mask of humility into pieces. And put on the mask of arrogance if needed.', 2874, 0), (56221, 'You’ll feel afraid at times. You’ll feel weak at times. But remember, fear and weakness are not your enemies. They are forms of evolutionary wisdom in the face of danger. Take some time to assess the situation and shake the weakness and fear off your limbic system.', 2874, 0), (56222, 'At times, look back towards your ancient days, drink deep from the eternal fountain of wisdom long gone, and then look ahead.', 2874, 0), (56223, 'I cannot change the people around me, but I can change what kind of people are around me.', 11031, 0), (56224, 'Live every single moment of your life, for the one thing that is most precious to you.', 2874, 0), (56225, 'The negativity fuel and the winner rules', 5009, 0), (56226, 'Its not about what we take with us when we die,Its about what we leave behind.', 12703, 0), (56227, 'Religion is an experience, not a bunch of doctrines.', 2874, 0), (56228, 'There is no force in the universe that can harm you, unless you allow it to.', 2874, 0), (56229, 'Humans are born with a hodge-podge of various brain circuits, that possess the seeds of peace, fear, love,